{"tid":1724132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得三十歲以上會手停口停，理財都理得幾撚失敗","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:49:53.000Z","uid":79927,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9fb442b66e254beb7ff6f287a0793fb3eaf93d","tid":1724132,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"三十歲人，當佢21歲畢業，即係做咗差唔多十年野<br />\n如果一冇咗份工就會下個月即刻比唔到家用交唔到租養唔到仔女<br />\n即係佢過去十年都係月月清冇儲錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果話要供樓，一冇咗份工就會即刻供唔到樓<br />\n咁就仲on9<br />\n即係佢以前all in買樓然後借到盡去供樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />稍為有啲風險管理意識都唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲人根本遲早都會死，經濟一轉差咪又係會比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時咪又係會手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86169763e2d784d30482413831fe201196919341","tid":1724132,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾低學歷藍屍"},{"pid":"dc3fd80f024ee7b27b37a9d573378801dc5aefa9","tid":1724132,"uid":51920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"三十歲人都要食飯 應唔應該反省下"},{"pid":"e9091faaab53cfeecb5cae56a7a0de4cea8ae99d","tid":1724132,"uid":261252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"同意到仆街"}]}